channel.title: How Do I make it so other people can join
channel.description: How Do I make It so other people can join my server? I have my No-Ip program running while I'm playing and other people cant connect to my server. My server Ip is Hellzend100.no-ip.org, My No-Ip I added my Ip to the No-Ip program and made the server Hellzend100.no-ip.org. Can somebody please eplain what you have to do in the first place to make it so others can join your server so then I can do what I haven't done.

item.title: How Do I make it so other people can join
item.dc:creator: @sgt_yoshi sgt yoshi
item.description:
@sgt_yoshi wrote:

In the character file…

[SKILLS] character-skill = 0.100.........16381500 character-skill = 1.100.........14910000 character-skill = 2.100.........14910000 character-skill = 3.100.........15298155 character-skill = 4.100.........14910000 character-skill = 5.100.........14910000 character-skill = 6.100.........14910000 character-skill = 7.100.........14910000 character-skill = 8.100.........14910000 character-skill = 9.100.........14910000 character-skill = 10.100........14910000 character-skill = 11.100........14910000 character-skill = 12.100........14910000 character-skill = 13.100........14910000 character-skill = 14.100........14910000 character-skill = 15.100........14910000 character-skill = 16.100........15810000 character-skill = 17.100........14910000 character-skill = 18.100........14910000 character-skill = 19.100........14910000 character-skill = 20.100........14910000 character-skill = 21.100........14910000 character-skill = 22.100........14910000 character-skill = 23.100........14910000 character-skill = 24.2200.......0

Character skill = # is the ID of the skill.

100 is the level, and the last portion is the experience in the skill.

Yours may not be the same as mine, but now you know what the numbers represent.
